---
// Case-study callout band. "Read full case study" points to /blog;
// swap to the specific post once that page is ready.
---

<section class="results">
  <div class="results__inner">
    <div class="results__left">
      <div class="eyebrow eyebrow--light">Case Study</div>
      <h2 class="rk-h2 rk-h2--light">
        The Results Speak <span class="rk-accent-lime">Louder Than We Do</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="rk-lede rk-lede--light">
        This podiatry clinic wanted to move beyond referrals. With a strategic paid-search campaign, their bookings grew <b>63%</b> — with Google Ads now driving <b>189 new patients</b> per month.
      </p>

      <div class="results__meta">
        <div class="rm"><span>Industry</span><b>Podiatry</b></div>
        <div class="rm"><span>Timeframe</span><b>90 days</b></div>
        <div class="rm"><span>Channel</span><b>Google Ads + Local SEO</b></div>
      </div>

      <a class="rk-btn rk-btn--outline-light" href="/blog">
        Read the full case study &rarr;
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="results__right">
      <div class="result-card">
        <div class="result-card__tag">Before · After</div>
        <div class="result-card__row">
          <div class="rc__block">
            <div class="rc__small">New patients / mo</div>
            <div class="rc__num">116</div>
            <div class="rc__label">Before</div>
          </div>
          <div class="rc__arrow" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</div>
          <div class="rc__block rc__block--after">
            <div class="rc__small">New patients / mo</div>
            <div class="rc__num">189</div>
            <div class="rc__label">After <span class="rc__delta">+63%</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="result-card__quote">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 20 14" width="20" height="14" aria-hidden="true">
            <path d="M0 14V7a7 7 0 0 1 7-7v3a4 4 0 0 0-4 4h4v7H0zm10 0V7a7 7 0 0 1 7-7v3a4 4 0 0 0-4 4h4v7h-7z" fill="#0E7C86" />
          </svg>
          <p>
            "Our schedule is finally full every week. Kevin doesn't just run ads — he taught us how to think about growth."
          </p>
          <div class="result-card__author">
            <div class="avatar" aria-hidden="true"></div>
            <div>
              <b>Dr. Sarah Chen</b>
              <span>Owner, Cascade Podiatry</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .results {
    background: linear-gradient(140deg, var(--teal-700) 0%, var(--teal) 100%);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 72px var(--pad);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .results::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 90% 100%, rgba(201, 242, 77, 0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 60% at 0% 0%, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05) 0%, transparent 60%);
  }
  .results__inner {
    position: relative;
    max-width: var(--maxw);
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 64px;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .results__meta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 28px;
    margin: 28px 0 28px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .rm {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .rm span {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal-100);
  }
  .rm b {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .result-card {
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--ink-900);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: 28px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
  }
  .result-card__tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--teal);
    background: var(--teal-50);
    padding: 5px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }
  .result-card__row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr auto 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
  }
  .rc__block {
    padding: 16px;
    background: var(--paper);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
  }
  .rc__block--after {
    background: var(--teal-50);
    border: 1px solid var(--teal-100);
  }
  .rc__small {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-500);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .rc__num {
    font-size: 40px;
    font-weight: 800;
    letter-spacing: -0.035em;
    color: var(--ink-900);
    margin: 4px 0 2px;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .rc__block--after .rc__num { color: var(--teal); }
  .rc__label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-500);
    font-weight: 600;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .rc__delta {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #1f9e63;
    padding: 2px 6px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: color-mix(in oklab, #1f9e63 15%, white);
  }
  .rc__arrow {
    color: var(--teal);
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .result-card__quote {
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-100);
    position: relative;
  }
  .result-card__quote svg { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .result-card__quote p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    color: var(--ink-700);
    margin: 0 0 16px;
    font-style: italic;
  }
  .result-card__author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .avatar {
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--teal) 0%, var(--teal-200) 100%);
    border: 2px solid #fff;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .result-card__author b {
    display: block;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--ink-900);
  }
  .result-card__author span {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--ink-500);
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .results__inner {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }
  }
</style>
